Package org.cougaar.planning.ldm.measure

Interface Summary
BinaryOperator<M extends Measure> An operator that can be applied on two measures.
Conversion Abstraction of a conversion function from one unit of measure to another compatible unit of measure.
Derivative Interface for all Derivative or "Rate" Measures.
Measure Base interface for all Measure classes.
Rate Implemented by Measures which represent derivatives with respect to Duration.
UnaryOperator<M extends Measure> An operator that can be applied on a single measure.

InvalidBoundsException
